    "description": "写在最前面：<br>这是一款由一个人独立开发的独立游戏，如果游戏中碰到什么问题欢迎留言或者联系我。月球之谜使用虚幻引擎（Unreal® Engine）。Unreal®是Epic Games, Inc.在美国及其他地区的商标或注册商标。Unreal® Engine，版权1998 – 2024, Epic Games, Inc.版权所有。<br><br><br>故事背景：<br>人类在近年来的科技发展，已经实现月球殖民。同时，人类成立了联合科研机构，在月球建立了基地，进行科学研究。并且人类通过可控核聚变技术，成功从月球岩石中获取燃料进行核聚变，实现了无线供能和人造引力大气层，确保基地周围的氧气和压力保持近地水平。<br>由于月球运行出现异常，人类在月球的基地频繁受到不明生物的攻击。目前人类已经撤离了月球基地的相关工作人员，现派你作为军方的前哨兵前往月球侦查异常问题，并想办法解决发现的异常。<br><br>阶段一：生存<br>你将从月球基地醒来，你需要做的第一件事是维持供给和能源，想办法生存下来。探索和采集原材料，生产制造必需品。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335540/extras/4497c74877774b526441db609582e060.poster.avif?t=1715870952\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335540/extras/4497c74877774b526441db609582e060.webm?t=1715870952\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335540/extras/4497c74877774b526441db609582e060.mp4?t=1715870952\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>阶段二：守护<br>宇宙飞船停靠的周边经常有不明生物来袭，你需要加强防御炮塔工事修建，确保宇宙飞船不被毁灭，你才有回地球的希望。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335540/extras/2ed9a7738fbd0e28c22ea479574ea4f5.poster.avif?t=1715870952\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335540/extras/2ed9a7738fbd0e28c22ea479574ea4f5.webm?t=1715870952\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335540/extras/2ed9a7738fbd0e28c22ea479574ea4f5.mp4?t=1715870952\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>阶段三：探索<br>你通过发展自己的装备和补给品，增加续航以后，可以前往周边的建筑设施和神秘地点，探索宝藏以及发现异常内容和神秘空间，并解决异常危机。同时，可以建立分支基地建筑，让自己能够临时落脚。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335540/extras/80f54c2c31f45c22920afa379dcee753.poster.avif?t=1715870952\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335540/extras/80f54c2c31f45c22920afa379dcee753.webm?t=1715870952\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335540/extras/80f54c2c31f45c22920afa379dcee753.mp4?t=1715870952\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>阶段四：解决异常<br>你会发现不同的神秘BOSS，并集合BOSS的掉落物品，开启隐藏空间，解决最终问题，重返地球，或者继续月球休闲旅行。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335540/extras/8394bda87acffc458ec8e6fd64dfe844.poster.avif?t=1715870952\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335540/extras/8394bda87acffc458ec8e6fd64dfe844.webm?t=1715870952\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335540/extras/8394bda87acffc458ec8e6fd64dfe844.mp4?t=1715870952\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
